            <lg xml:id="TK1294">
<l>iṉiyaṉṉa niṉṉōṭu cūḻvāryār neñcē </l>
<l> tuṉiceytu tuvvāykāṇ maṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my soul! you would not first seem sulky and then enjoy (him) who then would in future consult you about such things?</l>
            </lg>
